        // hack for back button - get values from cookie
        function getModels() {
            var cookieValue = $.cookie("duPontSearch");
            if (cookieValue) {
                var make = GetParameterValues('make', 'duPontSearch');
                if (make)
                {
                    // re-loading model if we have a cookie make value
                    LoadModels();

                    // is there a model?
                    var model = GetParameterValues('model', 'duPontSearch');
                    if (model)
                    {
                        // set it to selected
                        // alert(model);
                        // have o set a timeout on this... have to "wait" for the dropdown to be rebuilt...
                        setTimeout(function () {
                            var ddModel = $("#mainContentPlaceholder_topModelSelect");
                            ddModel.val(model);
                        }, 2000);
                    }
                }
            }
        }
      
        function GetParameterValues(param, cookiename) {
            var url = $.cookie(cookiename).split('&amp;');
            for (var i = 0; i &lt; url.length; i++) {
                var urlparam = url[i].split('=');
                if (urlparam[0] == param) {
                    return urlparam[1];
                }
            }
        };

        <script type="text/javascript">
         $("body").on("change", "#mainContentPlaceholder_topMakeSelect", function () {
            LoadModels();
        });
    

        function LoadModels() {
            $("#mainContentPlaceholder_topModelSelect").empty();
            $("#mainContentPlaceholder_topModelSelect").append("&lt;option value=''&gt;All Models&lt;/option&gt;");
            var make = $("#mainContentPlaceholder_topMakeSelect option:selected").val();
            if (make !== undefined &amp;&amp; make !== '') {
                $.getJSON(GLOBALSITEROOT + "v1/makes/" + make + "/models?inventory=true", function (data) {

                    var model = $("#mainContentPlaceholder_topModelSelect");

                    $.each(data, function (key, val) {
                        model.append("&lt;option value='" + val + "'&gt;" + val + "&lt;/option&gt;");
                    });

                    // checking model size first or it throws...
                    if (model.Length &gt; 0 &amp;&amp; model[0] !== undefined &amp;&amp; model[0] !== "") {
                        model[0].selectedIndex = 0;
                        model[0].jcf.buildDropdown();
                        model[0].jcf.refreshState();
                    }
                });
            }
        }

        $("div.page").on("click", "div.xToClose", function (event) {
            $("section.invalidZip").css({ "visibility": "hidden" });
            $("div.greyedWindow").css({ "visibility": "hidden", "z-index": "-100" });
        });
        function validateZip() {
            var zipcode = $('#mainContentPlaceholder_topZipCode').val();
            if ((/^\d{5}?$/).test(zipcode) | zipcode == 'Enter a Zip Code') {
                return true;
            } else {
                $('#mainContentPlaceholder_popupZipCode').val(zipcode);
                $("section.invalidZip").css({ "visibility": "visible", "z-index": 1000 });
                $("div.greyedWindow").css({ "visibility": "visible", "z-index": 999 });
                return false;
            }
        }
        function validateZip2() {
            var zipcode = $('#mainContentPlaceholder_popupZipCode').val();
            if ((/^\d{5}?$/).test(zipcode)) {
                $('#mainContentPlaceholder_topZipCode').val(zipcode);
                return true;
            } else {
                return false;
            }
        }

        function validateMake() {
            var make = $('#mainContentPlaceholder_topMakeSelect').val();
            make = $.trim(make);
            if (make !== undefined &amp;&amp; make !== '') {
                return true;
            } else {
                $('#error').html("&lt;span style='color: #FF6666;'&gt;- Please select a make&lt;/span&gt;");
                return false;
            }
        }

        function validateForm() {

            var make = $('#mainContentPlaceholder_topMakeSelect').val();
            var zip = $('#mainContentPlaceholder_topZipCode').val();
            var error = '';
            var makeValid = false;
            var zipValid = false;

            if (make === undefined || make === '') {
                makeValid = false;
                error = "- Please select a Make.";
            }
            else {
                makeValid = true;   
            }

            if (zip === undefined || zip === '' || zip === 'Enter a Zip Code') 
            {   
                zipValid = false;
                error = "- Please Enter a Zip code.";
            }
            else 
            {
                zipValid = true;
                //if ((/^\d{5}?$/).test(zip))
                //{
                //    zipValid = true;
                //}
                //else {
                //    zipValid = false;
                //    error = "- Please Enter a Zip code.";
                //}
            } 
            
            // confirm(zipValid + ' ' + makeValid);
            if (zipValid &amp;&amp; makeValid)
            {
                return true;
            }
            else
            {
                $('#error').html("&lt;span style='color: #FF6666;'&gt;" + error + "&lt;/span&gt;");
                return false;
            }
        }
        </script>

         <div>
          <p>
           duPont REGISTRY: A Buyers Guide of Fine Automobiles is the premiere luxury marketplace to buy exotic cars or sell your car.  
                Whether you are looking for new or used sports cars, exotic cars, luxury cars, supercars, duPont REGISTRY will have it for sale. 
                Nowhere else can you access such a vast selection of unique and exclusive cars in a navigable and simplified way, all in one single location. 
                Collectors, celebrities and enthusiasts alike acknowledge duPont REGISTRY for being a necessity in the automobile buying process. 
                As well as vehicles, duPont REGISTRY also caters to the needs of the buyer by offering quality selections of wheels, car accessories, aftermarket parts, shipping options and much more. 
                Go ahead, start your search for that dream car or finally get around to listing your car for sale with a
           <a href="http://blog.dupontregistry.com/news/dupont-registry-promo-code/" id="mainContentPlaceholder_hlPromo" style="float: none; color: #990000;" target="_blank" title="Save with our duPont Registry Promo Code">
            duPont Registry promo code
           </a>
           . 
                What ever car you're in the market for duPont Registry can help you find it.
           <br/>
           <br/>
           Dont take our word for it. Look what our customers think.
           <br/>
           To whom it may concern:
           <br/>
           This letter is to express my appreciation to the duPont Registry staff for their efforts.  I recently sold a 1964 Porsche 356C coupe as a direct result of advertising through the duPont Registry, the magazine publication of duPont Publications, Inc.  The duPont Registry reaches a world wide group of qualified buyers of exotic, luxury, and collector's vehicles.  My advertisement ran in their October, November, and December issues (2014), the annual months of valuable exposure to the automobile auction market.  Sharing advertising space with professional dealers and brokers gave me access to a limited but prestigious buyer group.
                The magazine's advertisement space that was provided for me equaled that of the dealers and brokers.  I enjoyed numerous referrals through secure email notices; my following up on the referrals was simplified through duPont Registry.  I contacted those who expressed interest, and informed them of my advertisement in the duPont Registry web site, which described the car in detail (photographs, description, technical specifications, and the vehicles history).  The web site advertisement (which ran until the car was sold) was changed, corrected, or modified at my requests; all responses by the magazine staff were timely or immediate.
                When the duPont Registry initially exposed my car to the collector's market, I received many requests for more detailed information.  Word of mouth then became apparent by the increased number of inquiries I received.  Thankfully, I was able to communicate the true nature of this exceptional example of the Porsche 356C, by referring prospective buyers to duPont Registry's web site advertisement of my car.
                This was the second time I enjoyed a professional relationship with duPont Registry.  By selling two rare vehicles to members of a limited group, I have grown to appreciate the skill and knowledge that the staff posses.  The people at duPont Restry displayed the friendly cooperation and coordination required to do business with a difficult elitist group of buyers.
           <br/>
           <br/>
           Respectfully,
           <br/>
           Victor C. De Coudreaux
